<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>We're Currently Closed</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="closed-message">
      <h2>🔒 We're Currently Closed</h2>
      <p>
        <strong>Sorry, we are not available at this moment.</strong>
      </p>
      <p>
        Current time: <strong><%= currentTime %></strong>
      </p>
      <p>
        We are only available Monday to Friday, 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM (UTC-5)
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.95rem; opacity: 0.9;">
        Please come back during our working hours, and we'll be happy to assist you!
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="content" style="margin-top: 2rem; text-align: center;">
      <h3>In the Meantime...</h3>
      <p>
        You can still reach us via email at <strong>info@workinghoursapp.com</strong>
        or leave a message, and we'll get back to you as soon as possible.
      </p>
      <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
        <a href="/" style="color: #667eea; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">← Back to Home</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2024 Working Hours App. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
